Glitter Boy Pilot
Glitter Boy Pilots operate the most feared single-warrior weapon system in
North America: the Glitter Boy power armor, a pre-Rifts relic whose laser-
reflective chrome surface and Boom Gun make it a legend on any battlefield.

Glitter Boy Pilots choose from Weapons, Physical, Military, and Pilot skill
categories. They are trained to get maximum performance from their armor and
to use the Boom Gun effectively despite its severe recoil.

Note: Glitter Boy power armor is among the rarest equipment in the game world.
Characters begin with access to the armor but its recovery and maintenance are
ongoing story concerns.

Attribute requirements: IQ 9, PS 12, PP 10.
Starting equipment: Glitter Boy power armor, Boom Gun with ammunition, repair
toolkit, and basic survival gear.
